            code: `Logits (pre-softmax scores):
  z = f_θ(x)  where f_θ is the CNN/ViT

Softmax probabilities:
  pᵢ = e^(zᵢ) / Σⱼ e^(zⱼ)

Cross-entropy loss (for true class y):
  L = -log(p_y) = -z_y + log(Σⱼ e^(zⱼ))

Top-1 / Top-5 accuracy:
  Top-1: predicted class = true class?
  Top-5: true class in top 5 predictions?

Label smoothing (regularization):
  y_smooth = (1-ε)·y_onehot + ε/K
  Prevents overconfidence.`,
