            code: `Architecture (2D U-Net):
  Encoder:
    Input: 572×572 grayscale (CT/MRI slice)
    Conv → ReLU → Conv → ReLU
    MaxPool (2×2) → feature maps halved
    Repeat 4× with doubling channels

  Bottleneck:
    1024 channels at 28×28

  Decoder:
    Up-conv (2×2) + skip connection
    Concatenate with corresponding encoder features
    Conv → ReLU → Conv → ReLU
    Repeat 4× with halving channels

  Output: 388×388 segmentation mask
    Background = 0, Tumor = 1, Edema = 2

Loss: Dice Loss + Cross-Entropy
  Dice = 2·|pred ∩ true| / (|pred| + |true|)
  → Handles class imbalance in small lesions`,
