            code: `FORWARD PASS:
  x → [W₁] → a₁ → [W₂] → a₂ → [W₃] → ŷ → Loss

BACKWARD PASS (chain rule):
  ∂L/∂W₃ = ∂L/∂ŷ · ∂ŷ/∂W₃
  ∂L/∂W₂ = ∂L/∂ŷ · ∂ŷ/∂a₂ · ∂a₂/∂W₂
  ∂L/∂W₁ = ∂L/∂ŷ · ∂ŷ/∂a₂ · ∂a₂/∂a₁ · ∂a₁/∂W₁

Output layer error:
  δᴸ = ∇ₐL ⊙ f'(zᴸ)

Hidden layer error:
  δˡ = ((Wˡ⁺¹)ᵀ δˡ⁺¹) ⊙ f'(zˡ)

Weight gradient:
  ∂L/∂Wˡ = δˡ (aˡ⁻¹)ᵀ`,
